column2: SELECT n.objid as sdssid, n.distance, p.ra AS ra, p.dec AS dec, (p.psfmag_u-p.extinction_u) as uPSFMag, (p.psfmag_g-p.extinction_g) as gPSFMag, (p.psfmag_r-p.extinction_r) as rPSFMag, (p.psfmag_i-p.extinction_i) as iPSFMag, (p.psfmag_z-p.extinction_z) as zPSFMag, p.psfmagerr_u as uPSFMagErr, p.psfmagerr_g as gPSFMagErr, p.psfmagerr_r as rPSFMagErr, p.psfmagerr_i as iPSFMagErr, p.psfmagerr_z as zPSFMagErr, (p.fibermag_u-p.extinction_u) as uFiberMag, (p.fibermag_g-p.extinction_g) as gFiberMag, (p.fibermag_r-p.extinction_r) as rFiberMag, (p.fibermag_i-p.extinction_i) as iFiberMag, (p.fibermag_z-p.extinction_z) as zFiberMag, p.fibermagerr_u as uFiberMagErr, p.fibermagerr_g as gFiberMagErr, p.fibermagerr_r as rFiberMagErr, p.fibermagerr_i as iFiberMagErr, p.fibermagerr_z as zFiberMagErr, p.flags, p.type INTO mydb.lsdr6_w1w2_SDSS FROM mydb.lsdr6_w1w2_coords AS m CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (m.ra_#, m.dec_#, #) AS n JOIN PhotoObjAll AS p ON n.objid = p.objid WHERE p.flags&# = # AND p.flags&# = # AND p.flags&# = # AND p.flags&# = #
